# React Web Application with Routing and Form Logic

A medium-sized single-page React application featuring a multi-section landing page and additional Sign Up and Login pages.
The project focuses on component-based architecture, client-side routing using React Router, and basic JavaScript-driven form logic (email validation and event handling).
Built with reusable functional components and structured following modern React best practices.

# Live Demo
(https://frontend-portfolio-react-website.netlify.app/)

# Features
- Multi-section landing page (navigation, hero, body sections, footer)
- Client-side routing (React Router)
- Sign Up & Login pages with basic form validation
- JavaScript-driven UI interactions (email validation, button animation)
- Component-based architecture
- Responsive layout for desktop screens
- Clean and maintainable code structure

